{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata -->
{{Redirects|Template:Military|the WikiProject template|Template:WikiProject Military history|the infobox|Template:Infobox national military|the navbox|Template:Military and war}}
{{shortcut|Military|template=1}}
Examples:
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{armed forces|United States}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{armed forces|USA}}</nowiki>}}

Multiple uses of this template can increase the [[Wikipedia:Post-expand include size|Post-expand include size]] of the page. The following alternative can be used instead:

* {{tlx|armed forces|USA}} → {{armed forces|USA}} (426b)
* {{mlx|1=flagg|2=main|3=usl|4=avar=military|5=USA}} → {{#invoke:flagg|main|usl|avar=military|USA}} (287b)


